Two files associated with TCP wrappers is hosts.deny and hosts.allow files
Tcp wrappers will read the hosts.allow file first ,if the rules is not found it wil go with deny file.

Our requirement is  Deny all ,add only the required rules now and too to specified requirement.

hosts.deny :- ALL: ALL
hosts.allow  sshd: 10.  ---> will allow all the ipaddress starting with 10.
